column9:
Quality:Bad
Appearance:Looks ok, but is actually not
Suitability:Very thin seat

If you're searching for a sign to buy this, this isn't it. This swivel chair is poorly manufactured. You'll feel the base poking into your butt due to the thin material (this is a hazard tbh). There are missing screws, and the chair doesn't provide adequate back support. Despite being cheaper than other commercially available swivel chairs, I had hoped for something decent, but this falls far below that expectation. Do not make the same mistake I did; learn from my experience. I spent 919 pesos plus around 120 in shipping fees because I was desperate for a swivel chair. Avoid purchasing this chair at all costs
